					"documentation": "# Show Sale Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Non-registered* inserts a Sale **key**.\n2. *System* displays the information associated to a **Sale** with this *saleNumber* **key** (**title**, **description**, **status**, **price**,**publicationDate** and **file**).  \n\n## Alternative flow\n1. If there is any attribute with no value, the field will be empty."
