					"documentation": "# Register Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Non-registered* enters a **username**.\n2. *Non-registered* enters a **password** twice.\n3. *System* displays that the account was created.\n\n\n## Alternative flow (Account is not created)\n1. Username already exists.\n2. Password is not long enough\n3. Password does not match.\n",
