					"documentation": "# Add to whishlist Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Registered* clicks **Add to wishList** button.\n2. If the product is not in the whishlist *System* adds the product to this users **whislist**. If it is, the product is removed.\n3. *System* displays product was added or removed to whislist correctly.\n\n\n## Alternative flow\n1. The product was alredy bought.\n2. The product was removed from the sales list.",
